an style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">d) Endorsement on passport/receipt of purchase of foreign exchange</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">10)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of&nbsp;current social and professional status:</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">a) Service &ndash; Letter issued by the employer on company&rsquo;s official letterhead establishing the position of the employee in the company, years in service, grant of leave and salary certificate of the last three (3) months</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">b) Business/self-employed &ndash; Visa request letter on official letterhead with company registration papers</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">c) Student &ndash; Letter from school/university for grant of leave and copy of the valid ID</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#031b30\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">11)&nbsp;