al area of 301,340&nbsp;km2&nbsp;(116,350&nbsp;sq&nbsp;mi) and shares&nbsp;land borders with France, Switzerland, Austria, Slovenia. With around 60 million inhabitants, Italy is the third-most populous member state of the European Union. Rome&nbsp;is the capital and largest city of Italy.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#202122\">Italy has one of the most advanced economies in the world in terms of GDP. Italy is a&nbsp;founding&nbsp;and&nbsp;leading&nbsp;member of the&nbsp;European Union&nbsp;and the&nbsp;Schengen Area. As a reflection of&nbsp;its cultural wealth, Italy has the world&#39;s&nbsp;largest number&nbsp;of&nbsp;World Heritage Sites and is the&nbsp;fifth-most visited country.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Tourist&nbsp; Visa&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Work&nbsp; Visa &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Business Visa&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:22.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#548dd4\">Tourist&nbsp; Visa</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">1)&nbsp; &nbsp;Visa application form:&nbsp;to be filled out in English. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">2)&nbsp; &nbsp;Valid Passport&nbsp;- It must be valid for at least another three months starting from the day traveler depart from Italy (Current passport and old passports).</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">3)&nbsp;&nbsp; Two photographs</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">4)&nbsp;&nbsp; Travel health insurance&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">5)&nbsp; &nbsp;Proof of&nbsp;residence&nbsp;for nationals: a photocopy of the stay permit</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">6)&nbsp; Cover letter:&nbsp;explaining the purpose of the trip with itinerary detailed location(s) and duration of stay in Italy.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;7)&nbsp; Transportation&nbsp;return travel air ticket </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">8)&nbsp; Proof of the&nbsp;purpose of stay&nbsp;in Italy:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a)&nbsp; Proof of Hotel Booking Payment</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b)&nbsp; Certificate of a paid tourist package</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c)&nbsp; Day to day itinerary with ensured accommodation for the entire stay</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d)&nbsp; Complete Italian telephone contact and address for all accommodations</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Kindly note that the applications for Italian visas for tourist visits are processed as per the actual plan of travel and stay. Any change in the travel plan, cancellation/change of accommodations, etc. after submission of the application will lead to delay in the processing of the application. Similar changes after issuance of visa (if approved) for the Republic of Italy might lead to revocation of visa.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">9)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of sufficient funds:&nbsp;Traveler must be able to prove that you can sustain yourself financially for the duration of your trip.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a) Six (6) months bank statement (saving and current a/c, as applicable), and</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b) Three years Income Tax returns (personal and company, as applicable), and</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c) Copy of international credit card with six (6) months credit card statement and</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;d) Endorsement on passport/receipt of purchase of foreign exchange</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">10)&nbsp;&nbsp; Proof of&nbsp;current social and professional status:</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#031b30\">Marriage Certificate, Birth Certificate of Children&rsquo;s, etc.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span st